# Assets - Images

This folder contains product images for the Açaí Premium website.

## Recommended Image Sizes

- Product Cards: 400x400px (w=400)
- Gallery: 600x600px (w=600)
- Hero: 1920x1080px (w=1920)

## Image Sources

The website uses images from Unsplash (via CDN). To add custom images:
1. Add images to this folder
2. Update the `src` attributes in the HTML files
3. Use WebP format for better performance

